description:
Danny welcomes Kate Chastain from Bravo's Below Deck (new season premieres October 7 @ 9PM on Bravo)! They talk about the upcoming season, her thoughts on the current season of Below Deck Med, tablescapes, Housewives, and so much more!


Kate Interview: 4:28ish
